THE FOUR HORSE CYCLE (OS-SAFE VERSION)

PantheonOS uses a 4-stage maintenance cycle, each represented symbolically by a horse from the Stable:
	1.	Black Horse ‚Äî Diagnostics & Shadow Scan
Detects decay, drift, confusion, entropy.
	2.	Red Horse ‚Äî Tension & Battle Testing
Applies stressors; identifies weak or false structures.
	3.	White Horse ‚Äî Stabilization & Alignment
Brings coherence, unity, and clarity of mission.
	4.	Pale Horse ‚Äî Closure & Renewal
Ends the arc and prepares the field for new growth.

This cycle is symbolic, safe, and nonviolent.
It is an OS process, not mythology.

